Nance O'Neil https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nance_O%27Neil 0 Not to be confused with Australian-born British actress Nancy O'NeilGertrude Lamson (October 8, 1874 – February 7, 1965), known professionally as Nance O'Neil or Nancy O'Neil, was an American actress of stage and silent cinema of the early 20th century, dubbed the American Bernhardt. Not to_be_confused with Australian-born_British_actress_Nancy_O'NeilGertrude_Lamson ( October_8_,_1874 – February_7_,_1965 ) , known professionally as Nance_O'Neil or Nancy_O'Neil , was an_American_actress of stage and silent_cinema of the_early_20th_century , dubbed the_American_Bernhardt .
